{"tid":451983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"應該要頒諾貝爾和平獎俾呀朗","createTime":"2017-10-29T17:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T21:41:32.000Z","uid":44925,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"340c87cf5c5e301b429269a1a85abf7ae63a531e","tid":451983,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"利用足球獻出友誼之手<br />\n一腳一腳咁向加泰民眾顯示出馬德里政府既寬宏大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n當佢每一次射個波俾看台上加泰觀眾時<br />\n就有如當年甘地赤腳踩玻璃，以身作則，置個人榮辱於度外，用雙腳感動世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀朗既仁慈可能拯救左無數既生命，將數以萬計生命從流血衝突中拉返出黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果要起一座廟宇，唔係關帝廟，而應該係C朗廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a8f926a3d52a068e03855241144548b235f9c7","tid":451983,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48505d26b3c88509cb5f6b96e3df5fc9f54dd09","tid":451983,"uid":21894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:39:46.000Z","msg":"最後笑到我😂"},{"pid":"7f8a654e75fbfeb4761cf71062553a62b7566c4d","tid":451983,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:48:30.000Z","msg":"地球既和平靠C朗<br />\n<br />\n宇宙既和平靠屌奶星人"},{"pid":"7e14d8e6963661ff08fa4e9dfebaffd3cef6c942","tid":451983,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T21:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地球既和平靠C朗<br />\n<br />\n宇宙既和平靠屌奶星人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}